		<pb n="1"/>
          <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>St. Thomas</placeName> <date>5 July 1848</date></p>
		  <p><addressee>Revd Mr Leeser</addressee></p>
          <p rend="indent(2)">My Dr Sir</p>
          <p rend="indent(3)">Accompanying this letter you have the<lb/> manuscript copy of the Laws for the Government of the<lb/> Congregation of the Island which is entrusted to your<lb/> care for printing&#44; we require five hundred copies &#38; wish<lb/> them printed in pamphlet form neatly done up &#38; executed<lb/> with dispatch. I have assured my colleagues that you<lb/> would execute the order for a moderate price. We could have<lb/> them done for &#36;50 here this we considered too much&#8212;you will<lb/> please send them by 2 opportunities each with 250 copies.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">The slaves in the <placeName>Danish Colonies</placeName> were liberated<lb/> on the <date>3d Jun</date> at <placeName>St. Croix</placeName>&#44; &#38; yesterday here &#38; <placeName>St Johns</placeName>&#44; the Govern&#45;<lb/>ment at <placeName>St Croix</placeName> was faced by a demonstration of 7000 slaves<lb/> the opposing face very inadequate&#44; it was unexpected by the<lb/> Government &#38; Inhabitants &#38; appeared an organized affair&#44; some<lb/> excesses were committed there the particulars of which we have<lb/> not received. I am happy to state that it went off well<lb/> here&#44; the liberated only singing through the streets <date>8 July</date> the<lb/> excesses in <placeName>St Croix</placeName> are lamentable&#44; after the people were freed they<lb/> became lawless&#44; destroying property in every way setting fire &#38;<lb/> what could not be destroyed in this way&#44; they did so wantonly<lb/> by knocking in the heads of the Puncheons of Rum &#38; molasses<lb/> selling the <add>&#63;</add> of sugar over precipices thereby <add>&#63;</add> them &#38;<lb/> sending the sugar to the winds pulling down Houses &#38;c</p>
          <p rend="indent(8)">I am D Sir</p>
          <p rend="indent(9)"><persName role="author">A. Wolff</persName></p>

         </body>
